infos.value: ...A cave.
Minwu...
Once we pass through this cave, we will be in Wezette territory.
At last...
Muraga's wretches shouldn't follow us here...
Yeah. No one nipping at our tails for now, right?
Not after Gilgamesh's brutal demonstration.
All the same...
What troubles you?
I fear we will soon be visible to any guards posted by Wezette.
Even so, it's too late to turn back, right?
Not just for King Oelde's sake. Schuzelt is gravely injured too.
Then again, I guess we should be thankful Gilgamesh showed up when he did. If he hadn't, it would have been the end of us.
You're right.
Minwu... What do you know about Gilgamesh?
I have heard rumors about him.
He is a supreme being who rules over all kings and their dominions...
It seems the ring Father entrusted to me was in fact bequeathed to him by Gilgamesh.
That must make him our ally...right?
Let's keep moving, Lord Mont.
...Right.
